graph TD
    subgraph Frontend [React SPA (Vite)]
        UI[User Interface]
        SyncEngine[Local Sync Engine]
        Cache[(LocalStorage)]
    end

    subgraph Backend [Node.js Express Server]
        API[Express REST API]
        AuthSvc[Auth Service (JWT/bcrypt)]
        AISvc[Gemini AI Service]
        DBSvc[Supabase Service Role]
    end

    subgraph ThirdParty [External Services]
        Supabase[(Supabase PostgreSQL)]
        Gemini[Google Gemini API]
    end

    %% Frontend Internal Flow
    UI <-->|Reads/Writes| SyncEngine
    SyncEngine <-->|Caches Data| Cache

    %% Client to Server Flow
    SyncEngine -->|HTTP POST /api/auth/login| API
    SyncEngine -->|HTTP GET/POST /api/sync| API
    UI -->|HTTP POST /api/ai/infer-gender| API

    %% Server to External Flow
    AuthSvc -->|Validates & Hashes| API
    DBSvc -->|CRUD via Service Role| Supabase
    AISvc -->|API Key Auth| Gemini

    %% Internal Server Flow
    API --> AuthSvc
    API --> AISvc
    API --> DBSvc
